<subSubSection pageId="147" pageNumber="545" type="conservation">
<paragraph blockId="147.[1385,2593,293,680]" pageId="147" pageNumber="545">
<emphasis bold="true" box="[1387,1734,445,478]" pageId="147" pageNumber="545">Status and Conservation.</emphasis>
Classified as Data Deficient on The IUCN Red List. The Mount Kenya Mole Shrew has a very small distribution and a fragmented population. It is known from few museum specimens. Research is needed to determine the major threats that may affect the species.
</paragraph>
</subSubSection>
